content:
Analyze the following table and identify distinct logical tables within it.

Table HTML:
{cleaned_html}

For each distinct table you identify, provide:
1. table_range: The complete data range in Excel notation (e.g., "A1:G5") that includes all cells of the table
2. header_range: The header/title range in Excel notation (e.g., "A1:G1") that contains the column headers

Make sure to include all the cells that make up each table.

Return your response in the exact JSON format expected by the schema, with each table having both table_range and header_range fields.

example response:
{{"tables": [
        {{
            "table_range": "A1:G5",
            "header_range": "A1:G1",
        }}
    ]
}}
